            <div id="sm-cog-elements" class="noprint"></div>
            <div class="allset-page-heading"><h1>Reference:卓越汉语－公司实战篇</h1></div>
            <!-- subtitle -->
            <div id="contentSub" ></div>
            <!-- /subtitle -->
                        <div id="mw-content-text" lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr"><div class="mw-parser-output"><span class="plainlinks"><div class="floatright"><a href="http://www.amazon.cn/%E5%8D%93%E8%B6%8A%E6%B1%89%E8%AF%AD-%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8%E5%AE%9E%E6%88%98%E7%AF%87-%E8%83%A1%E7%81%B5%E5%9D%87/dp/B003QZWQ6M/ref=sr_1_1?ie=UTF8&amp;qid=1347863170&amp;sr=8-1" rel="nofollow"><img alt="Zhuoyue-hanyu-gongsi-shizhanpian.jpg" src="https://resources.allsetlearning.com/gramwiki/images/thumb/b/be/Zhuoyue-hanyu-gongsi-shizhanpian.jpg/300px-Zhuoyue-hanyu-gongsi-shizhanpian.jpg" decoding="async" width="300" height="411" srcset="https://resources.allsetlearning.com/gramwiki/images/thumb/b/be/Zhuoyue-hanyu-gongsi-shizhanpian.jpg/450px-Zhuoyue-hanyu-gongsi-shizhanpian.jpg 1.5x, https://resources.allsetlearning.com/gramwiki/images/thumb/b/be/Zhuoyue-hanyu-gongsi-shizhanpian.jpg/600px-Zhuoyue-hanyu-gongsi-shizhanpian.jpg 2x" /></a></div></span><p>The business Chinese textbook 《卓越汉语－公司实战篇》 is available only in China and has no official English name.
</p><div id="toc" class="toc"><input type="checkbox" role="button" id="toctogglecheckbox" class="toctogglecheckbox" style="display:none" /><div class="toctitle" lang="en" dir="ltr"><h2>Contents</h2><span class="toctogglespan"><label class="toctogglelabel" for="toctogglecheckbox"></label></span></div>
<ul>
<li class="toclevel-1 tocsection-1"><a href="./Reference:卓越汉语－公司实战篇#Grammar_Points_by_Chapter"><span class="tocnumber">1</span> <span class="toctext">Grammar Points by Chapter</span></a></li>
<li class="toclevel-1 tocsection-2"><a href="./Reference:卓越汉语－公司实战篇#Grammar_Point_References_to_This_Book"><span class="tocnumber">2</span> <span class="toctext">Grammar Point References to This Book</span></a></li>
</ul>
</div>

<h2><span class="mw-headline" id="Grammar_Points_by_Chapter">Grammar Points by Chapter</span></h2>
<ol><li>第1课初到公司
<ul><li>Conversation - Robert初到J&amp;G公司
<ul><li>这（不）是sb.第一次... It's not the first time for somebody to...</li>
<li><a href="Comparing_&quot;kending&quot;_&quot;queding&quot;_and_“yiding&quot;" title="Comparing &quot;kending&quot; &quot;queding&quot; and “yiding&quot;">肯定 certainly; undoubtedly; definitely</a></li>
<li><a href="&quot;Although&quot;_with_&quot;jinguan&quot;" class="mw-redirect" title="&quot;Although&quot; with &quot;jinguan&quot;">尽管 feel free to; do not hesitate to</a></li></ul></li>
<li>Culture - 中国人的称呼
<ul><li><a href="&quot;Both…_and…&quot;_with_&quot;ji...you&quot;" class="mw-redirect" title="&quot;Both… and…&quot; with &quot;ji...you&quot;">既...又... both...and...</a></li>
<li><a href="Expressing_&quot;from_this&quot;_with_&quot;youci&quot;" title="Expressing &quot;from this&quot; with &quot;youci&quot;">由此可见 from this; it can be seen that</a></li>
<li><a href="Using_&quot;dui&quot;#.E5.AF.B9.E2.80.A6.E2.80.A6.E6.9D.A5.E8.AF.B4" class="mw-redirect" title="Using &quot;dui&quot;">对...来说 for somebody</a></li>
<li><a href="Expressing_purpose_with_&quot;weile&quot;" title="Expressing purpose with &quot;weile&quot;">是为了 for the purpose of</a></li></ul></li>
<li>Context - 改革和开放
<ul><li><a href="&quot;Along_with…&quot;_Using_&quot;suizhe&quot;" class="mw-redirect" title="&quot;Along with…&quot; Using &quot;suizhe&quot;">随着 along with</a></li>
<li>归功于 give credit to</li>
<li><a href="Causative_verbs" title="Causative verbs">使 make; cause</a></li>
<li><a href="Emphasizing_a_negation_with_&quot;bing&quot;" title="Emphasizing a negation with &quot;bing&quot;">并 ＋ 不／没有 (emphasize the negation)</a></li>
<li><a href="Comparing_&quot;fan'er&quot;_and_“xiangfan&quot;" title="Comparing &quot;fan&#39;er&quot; and “xiangfan&quot;">相反 on the contrary</a></li></ul></li></ul></li>
<li>第2课会见客户
<ul><li>Conversation - 和经理会见重要客户
<ul><li>对...进行... conduct; execute; carry out</li>
<li><a href="Comparing_&quot;genju&quot;_and_&quot;ju&quot;" title="Comparing &quot;genju&quot; and &quot;ju&quot;">根据 according to</a></li>
